{"tid":127163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB：中資吞食港資市場","createTime":"2017-02-20T01:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T11:29:52.000Z","uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aaddd7af065cbf491ebfb486e7cface6d779d732","tid":127163,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T01:38:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://mytv.tvb.com/tc/cat_news/financemagazine/296171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmytv.tvb.com%2Ftc%2Fcat_news%2Ffinancemagazine%2F296171&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5PgROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=52755262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://mytv.tvb.com/tc/cat_news/financemagazine/296171</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/E0cao8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FE0cao8&h=7be86acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本港o既樓價雖然再創歷史o既新高 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/KdFfB2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FKdFfB2&h=b42a6137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近年中資機構參與本港賣地o既比率 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/taZBn5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FtaZBn5&h=a8e72b76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不斷上升 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/g9k8rI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fg9k8rI&h=9b3d5857&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部份o既成交價更大幅高過市場o既預期 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/PmIdhu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FPmIdhu&h=b3c22073&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中資佔整體入標者o既比例 <br />\n由一三年o既兩成六 <br />\n大幅升至舊年o既六成五 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/gneNlm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FgneNlm&h=b91a2683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而中資機構成功中標o既比率 <br />\n亦由一三年o既只有一成一 <br />\n逐年遞升至舊年o既兩成六 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/3Ir3Jc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F3Ir3Jc&h=de8c4c7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中資投地勇進 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/GE4th2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FGE4th2&h=d95aa5dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不惜以大幅高於市場預期o既價錢投地 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/BpvAgG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FBpvAgG&h=077288bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n接二連三 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/XoGYuO\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FXoGYuO&h=a502a1ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n創造o左一個新o既預期出o黎 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/IpZofx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FIpZofx&h=25b4e08f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而我o地o既香港o既發展商 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/hgEUa9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FhgEUa9&h=63bf65f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去跟隨呢個步伐呢先可以買到土地 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/rVVIit\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FrVVIit&h=681a7167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以呢個係一個預期走出o黎o既o野 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/Ffv0TA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FFfv0TA&h=e3dea2f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會創造o左一個新o既預期 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/60koag\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F60koag&h=977d1b59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身係測量師o既Lesly <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/a7UqHB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fa7UqHB&h=11369162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過去三年半都o係中資發展商果度工作 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/sS6NSB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FsS6NSB&h=9fe31047&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢分別代表過唔同o既中資機構投地 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/ao9K1y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fao9K1y&h=adea8655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你話佢貴啦 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/6vLDQe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F6vLDQe&h=14d652d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁　承受能力o係度喎 <br />\n買到喎 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/cCo3dH\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FcCo3dH&h=32d55594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁係咪貴呢？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/FkmVXi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FFkmVXi&h=63d9f987&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都有人買到喎 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/ONLLm0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FONLLm0&h=6aaf47e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個麵粉價我o地見到係貴o左 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/T5yxqs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FT5yxqs&h=fc015491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢o地第時要賺到錢 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/kcaiS5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FkcaiS5&h=0705d9c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要賣果個麵包一定要貴"},{"pid":"c2f46d9afb0f1ee18a9c8210d201dbbc144389ec","tid":127163,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T01:53:57.000Z","msg":"我唔係好明，你投個價大幅高過市場預期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之但係問題係你起樓起野，你係香港係零經驗，你覺得你個成本係可以低過其餘有經驗嘅大地產商？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後結果咪一係蝕錢，一係賺少勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a81a8e45f70259734c78af372b27c2eef1c5e9","tid":127163,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T01:57:27.000Z","msg":"再加埋而家美國開始加息，政府格硬通過東北發展，都算係增加緊土地供應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee53aa7615b4f4df2e00e7ebc528c2ed0be1e21","tid":127163,"uid":35205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:01:53.000Z","msg":"走資呀 <br />\n真係為賺錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cbd29280eb3a91a7b1c6aeadd7bda39902ad06f","tid":127163,"uid":33668,"like"